  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Prepare to drive in the EU after Brexit: lorry and goods vehicle drivers
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    What truck and lorry drivers from the UK may need to do to drive in the EU and EEA if the UK leaves the EU without a deal on 12 April 2019.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

